responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "84175999438C1E6B2E0FCEB94F2C191F", "Fair rising to you. Keep to the laws of the Seven and we\'ll have no quarrel. Crystal boom or not, the Kaelar Empire shall not descend into anarchy. Greed is the enemy within and will drive one to evil and eventually the gallows.")
